    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_2036-2056",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2036-2056",
      "markText": "真实GDP=名义GDP÷GDP平减指数。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2036&rangeEnd=2056",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2036&rangeEnd=2056"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_15405-15478",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "15405-15478",
      "markText": "名义GDP是按现期价格评价的物品与服务的生产，价格下降会导致名义GDP的下降，因此名义GDP在真实GDP的基础上下降10％，结果基本没有发生变化。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15405&rangeEnd=15478",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=15405&rangeEnd=15478"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_1285-1340",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1285-1340",
      "markText": "④净出口：等于国内生产并销售到国外的物品与服务的价值（出口）减国外生产并在国内销售的物品与服务的价值（进口）。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1285&rangeEnd=1340",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1285&rangeEnd=1340"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_1621-1656",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1621-1656",
      "markText": "GDP是流量而不是存量，是计算期内（如2012年）生产的最终产品价值。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1621&rangeEnd=1656",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1621&rangeEnd=1656"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_13_16124-16184",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "16124-16184",
      "markText": "如果美国的出口对真实汇率的弹性极低，外汇市场上的美元需求曲线就十分陡峭，美元供给的增加引起外汇市场上真实汇率的大幅度上升",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=16124&rangeEnd=16184",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=16124&rangeEnd=16184"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_991-1033",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "991-1033",
      "markText": "国内生产总值（GDP）指在某一既定时期一个国家内生产的所有最终物品与服务的市场价值。",
      "totalCount": 50,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=991&rangeEnd=1033",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=991&rangeEnd=1033"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_1913-1996",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1913-1996",
      "markText": "名义GDP（或货币GDP）是用生产物品和服务的当年价格计算的全部最终产品的市场价值。真实GDP是指用从前某一年的价格作为基期价格计算出来的当年全部最终产品的市场价值。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1913&rangeEnd=1996",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1913&rangeEnd=1996"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_5563-5599",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5563-5599",
      "markText": "消费指除了购买新住房，家庭用于物品和劳务的支出，是GDP的重要组成部分。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5563&rangeEnd=5599",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5563&rangeEnd=5599"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_1747-1789",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1747-1789",
      "markText": "GDP一般仅指市场活动导致的价值。家务劳动、自给自足生产等非市场活动不计入GDP中。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1747&rangeEnd=1789",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1747&rangeEnd=1789"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22624397_4_13835-13857",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "13835-13857",
      "markText": "联邦政府向一个美国老年人送去一张社会保障支票",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22624397&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=13835&rangeEnd=13857",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/edd321407159388dedd85d7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=13835&rangeEnd=13857"
    },
    {
